OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The music world has been paying tribute
OL,6, to singer Terry Hall, remembering The  
OL,7, Specials frontman as "truly one of the 
OL,8, greats" who had "a heart of gold".     
OL,10,FHits like Ghost Town, Gangsters and Too
OL,11,FMuch Too Young soundtracked British    
OL,12,Flife in the late 1970s and early 80s.  
OL,14,FTributes came from UB40, Boy George and
OL,15,FElvis Costello, who said his voice "was
OL,16,Fthe perfect instrument for the true and
OL,17,Fnecessary songs on The Specials".      
OL,19,FHe added: "That honesty is heard in so 
OL,20,Fmany of his songs in joy and sorrow."  
